From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Entrpi <entrpi@proton.me>
Date: Mon, 16 Feb 2026 17:44:53 +1100
Subject: [PATCH] sound: Add CIX Sky1 audio drivers

Add Sky1 I2S audio, DSP SoF, CIX IPBLOQ HDA controller,
HDMI/DisplayPort audio output, ACPI DMA range support,
and CIX Phecda HDA codec fixup.
